dc_title_s: Senior Centers, San Mateo County Sea Level Rise Vulnerability Assessment Project, 2010
dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents senior citizen centers (facilities that provide multiple services to older adults) in San Mateo County, California. Source: San Mateo County Health System. Acquired: August 2015. This layer is part of the San Mateo County Sea Level Rise Vulnerability Assessment Project. These data are intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.

dc_creator_sm: County of San Mateo Information Services Department
